The paper discusses exploration strategies for deep reinforcement learning, which is a topic that falls under the broad category of machine learning. This technique is relevant to several sub-fields within computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY).
